messages.content: I'm Panos Spiros, just a local worker around here. Nice to meet you. And you are...?
messages.speaker: Panos Spiros

messages.content: I am Tally, I do construction work
messages.speaker: Tally

messages.content: Oh, that's great. We could use some help around here with all the rebuilding efforts after the recent conflict. Tally, what made you decide to join the BLUFOR forces instead of continuing with your mechanical engineering career?
messages.speaker: Panos Spiros
